<v-dialog 
    v-model="visibleForm" 
    persistent 
    max-width="600">
        <v-card>
            <v-container>
                <v-row justify="center">
                    <v-card-tiitle class="headline">
                        Add/Modify vehicule.
                    </v-card-tiitle>
                </v-row>

                <v-row justify="center">
                    <v-card-text>
                        <v-container>

                            <v-row>
                                <v-col cols="12">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="License Plate"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>
                            </v-row>

                            <!-- Type -->
                            <v-row>
                                <v-col cols="4">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="Type"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>
                                <v-col cols="4">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="Marca"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>
                                <v-col cols="4">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="Model"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>                                                                        
                            </v-row>

                            <!-- Dimensions -->
                            <v-row>
                                <v-col cols="4">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="Height"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>
                                <v-col cols="4">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="Width"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>
                                <v-col cols="4">
                                    <v-text-field
                                        label="Depth"
                                        prepend-inner-icon="mdi-sign-caution"
                                        outlined>
                                    </v-text-field>
                                </v-col>                                                                        
                            </v-row>                            
                        </v-container>
                    </v-card-text>
                </v-row>

                <v-row justify="center">
                    <v-card-actions>
                    <v-spacer></v-spacer>
                    <v-btn color="blue darken-1" text @click="disabledForm">Close</v-btn>
                    <v-btn color="blue darken-1" text @click="saveVehicule">Save</v-btn>
                    </v-card-actions>
                </v-row>
            </v-container>
            


        </v-card>

</v-dialog>
